- Matplotlib, Seaborn

## ğŸ“Š Model Highlights
- Model: Logistic Regression
- Accuracy: ~87%
- Metrics: Confusion Matrix, ROC AUC, Classification Report

## ğŸ“ File Structure
- `Credit_Card_Fraud_Detection_LogReg.ipynb`: Main notebook
- `requirements.txt`: Dependencies
